To evaluate the usefulness of discourse motifs, we integrate them into three baseline models: Random Forest (RF) \citep{breiman2001random}, Graph Attention Network (GAT) \citep{velickovic2018graph}, and Longformer (LF) \citep{beltagy2020longformer}.
