\section{Difference Distributions Computed by Motif Frequency vs. MF-IDF Scores}

Figure \ref{fig:difference_dists_two_ways} presents two bar plots, illustrating (a) motif frequency and (b) MF-IDF scores of motifs across three domains. Notably, due to the IDF scaling, the latter plot exhibits a slightly less skewed pattern compared to the former plot.

